## Quick Start

```bash
npm install -D cosmux
```

```typescript
// vite.config.ts
import { cosmux } from 'cosmux/vite'

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [cosmux()]
})
```

```bash
# .env
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
```

Run `npm run dev` â€” the widget appears in the bottom-right corner.

